Solaris::DevLog version 1.00
============================

This module facilitates reading syslog messages via streams under Sun
Solaris, and supoprts the syslog door mechanism.  See the POD for more
details.

Special thanks to Netzwert AG <http://www.netzwert.ag> for supporting
the development of this module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the Solaris libraries:

   libdoor
   libthread

